tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE FinancialReports (
 report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 report_name VARCHAR(255),
 report_date DATE,
 report_parameters JSON
)

CREATE TABLE reports_metadata (
    metadata_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    report_id INT,
    metadata_key VARCHAR(50),
    metadata_value TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (report_id) REFERENCES financial_reports(report_id)
);

CREATE TABLE query_history (
    query_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    report_id INT,
    query TEXT,
    execution_date TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (report_id) REFERENCES financial_reports(report_id)
);

CREATE TABLE financial_reports (
 report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 report_date DATE,
 query_parameters VARCHAR(255),
 result_data TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE report_parameters (
 parameter_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 parameter_name VARCHAR(50),
 data_type VARCHAR(50),
 is_required BOOLEAN
)

CREATE TABLE sql_queries (
 query_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 query_text TEXT,
 query_result TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE database_connections (
 connection_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 connection_name VARCHAR(50),
 database_url VARCHAR(255),
 is_active BOOLEAN
)

CREATE TABLE FinancialReports (
 report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 report_name VARCHAR(50),
 report_date DATE,
 query_parameters TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE Queries (
 query_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 query_text TEXT,
 query_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE Parameters (
 parameter_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 parameter_name VARCHAR(50),
 parameter_type VARCHAR(20),
 parameter_value TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE Users (
 user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 username VARCHAR(50),
 access_level VARCHAR(20)
)

CREATE TABLE Log (
 log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 log_date TIMESTAMP,
 message TEXT
)
